---
title: Pork, Mushroom & Rosemary Pie with Parmesan Mash Topping & Balsamic Salad
description: Sometimes only a pie will do. Satisfy that craving for something warm and comforting with this rich, cheesy mash-topped
number with mushrooms. It's just like Nonna used to make (but better!).
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-rosemary-pie-f469bd8a.jpg
